# Frontend TALL e Widget

- **Accessibilità**: WCAG 2.1 AA; focus management/ARIA; ridotto movimento.
- **Livewire 3 + Alpine**: componenti accessibili; evita JS non necessario.
- **Tailwind**: usa design tokens/varianti; dark mode opzionale.
- **Widget web**: theming/branding, SDK eventi, quick‑actions mediate dal backend con JWT breve + HMAC.

### Percorsi
- Blade/Livewire: [backend/resources/views](mdc:backend/resources/views)
- JS/CSS: [backend/resources/js](mdc:backend/resources/js), [backend/resources/css](mdc:backend/resources/css)
- Widget: [backend/public/widget](mdc:backend/public/widget)